    <span class="step-badge badge-seq">SEQUENTIAL</span>
  </div>
  <div class="step-desc">Orders via CLOB API on-chain. Slippage monitored. Auto-hedge if conditions shift pre-settlement.</div>
  <div class="step-progress"><div class="step-progress-bar" id="prog-5" style="width:0%"></div></div>
</div>

<div class="pipeline-step" id="step-6" onclick="setActiveStep(6)">
  <div class="step-header">
    <span class="step-num">6</span>
    <span class="step-name">Compound</span>
    <span class="step-badge badge-iter">ITERATIVE</span>
  </div>
  <div class="step-desc">5 agents extract loss cause + prevention, save to knowledge base. Future scans search past cases first.</div>
